{"ID":"20241011005946-mkvbkpe","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20241011005946-mkvbkpe","title":"The Politic Science","type":"doc","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-ra2eh3i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-ra2eh3i","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Untitled.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/notion/aa/aa934708c6ad86fa71f400d33d6a1da2.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-rghe9mv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-rghe9mv","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Untitled 1.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/notion/ff/ffa24f93e0aaa95980d891bef6271912.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-n4d7wf7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-n4d7wf7","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"This book lists several question before the book, which can help me to better understand the information framework."}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-f4bxwr4","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-f4bxwr4","updated":"20241011010424"}},{"ID":"20241011010424-23hzuer","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-23hzuer","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"GPT:"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-jvbamy3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-jvbamy3","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当谈论马基雅维利和孔子的差异时，以下是一些重要的方面："}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-e5bhf8q","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-e5bhf8q","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-94a6bqh","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-94a6bqh","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-f6y394z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-f6y394z","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"政治观点：马基雅维利的政治观点强调现实主义和权谋手段，主张统治者应该使用各种手段来巩固自己的权力。相比之下，孔子的政治观点更加强调仁爱、道德和人德，他认为领导者应该以德治国，以身作则，影响他人。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-axg3h0x","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-axg3h0x","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-838qfcd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-838qfcd","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"道德观念：马基雅维利的观点被认为相对冷酷无情，强调在政治领域不择手段。而孔子强调仁义道德，强调个人修养和社会公德。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-idf6rgk","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-idf6rgk","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-vjqx2dx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-vjqx2dx","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"倡导的政治体制：马基雅维利主张君主制，认为强力统治是保持社会稳定的关键。而孔子主张君主应该行使仁德来领导人民，同时推崇贤明的君主。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-8zap9xq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-8zap9xq","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-p6up8eo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-p6up8eo","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对权力的看法：马基雅维利认为权力是自私和不可避免的，需要通过策略来保持。孔子则主张领导者应该以仁爱、谦逊和智慧来行使权力。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-hxpj7jd","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-hxpj7jd","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-vjajlnm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-vjajlnm","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对人性的理解：马基雅维利认为人性自私和腐败，强调人们在追求私利时可能会采取不道德的行为。孔子则相信人性本善，只要受到正确的教育和引导，人们可以成为更好的人。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-bjy79wb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-bjy79wb","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这些差异反映了他们的不同时代、文化和价值观，使他们的思想在政治、伦理和社会观念上存在显著差异。"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-9ys08hr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-9ys08hr","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在政治上，洛克和卢梭也有一些显著的不同之处："}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-i4o2kl3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-i4o2kl3","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-fcbk7qv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-fcbk7qv","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-60i9sf8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-60i9sf8","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"政治权力来源：洛克认为政治权力来自人民的授予，政府是为了保护人民的权利而存在，人民有权利反抗不公正的政府。他的政治理念强调个人权利和自由。卢梭则认为政治权力来自普遍意愿，政府是代表全体人民的意志，但他也强调人民的参与和控制政府的重要性。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-qwq4fcn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"Mi4=","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-qwq4fcn","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-tays65s","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-tays65s","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"统治者合法性：洛克的政治理念认为统治者的合法性取决于人民的同意和支持，他主张君主应受宪法限制。而卢梭认为政府的合法性来自于人民的一致意愿，但他也提出了更为集中的统治方式，认为政府应该具有更强大的权力来实现公共利益。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-0mi0icn","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"My4=","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-0mi0icn","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-aa195wa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-aa195wa","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"社会契约：虽然洛克和卢梭都提出了社会契约理论，但洛克的社会契约理论更加强调个人权利和限制政府权力的目的，而卢梭的社会契约理论则更强调人民共同参与政治决策，实现普遍意愿。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-hqa43e6","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NC4=","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-hqa43e6","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-a3y8k24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-a3y8k24","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"政府功能：洛克主张政府应该是有限的，主要任务是保护个人权利和财产。卢梭则认为政府应该是强大的，以实现公共利益和整体社会的福祉。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-vromz83","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Delimiter":46,"Marker":"NS4=","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-vromz83","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-exiiv72","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-exiiv72","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"社会不平等：洛克对社会不平等的看法较为冷静，认为一定程度的不平等是合理的。卢梭则强调社会不平等的不公正性，他对财富积累和私有财产制度持批评态度。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-7h4te8t","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-7h4te8t","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"这些政治上的不同观点反映了洛克和卢梭在政治哲学上的差异，他们的思想对于政治制度、社会秩序和政府职能的理解产生了深远的影响。"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-9l3lutk","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-9l3lutk","updated":"20241011010424"}},{"ID":"20241011010424-ehjxajh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-ehjxajh","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"洛克诉诸财产权，霍布斯诉诸恐惧"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-akhstst","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-akhstst","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Untitled 2.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/notion/96/9616f45b7c52c85d81360cbe2aa8856b.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-a0iv6wm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-a0iv6wm","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"Untitled 3.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"assets/notion/0e/0e4294e73a250f6d5bc9f26decb32b61.png"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-r14eqll","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-r14eqll","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-iqjtdmv","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-iqjtdmv","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-xctji6j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-xctji6j","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有的国家拥有很多民族，有的民族分裂成许多国家。民族是生物学的概念，而国家除此之外还包括经济，文化，宗教的范畴。民族认同是国家的重要组成部分，很大程度上影响着国家的运行，比如对德意志民族认同催生了德国的统一，欧洲民族意识的觉醒影响罗马帝国的分裂。但多民族的强烈整合似乎也促使了苏联的解体，阿拉伯人有许多国家，犹太人甚至在几十年前才组建了国家。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-k7r5ii4","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-k7r5ii4","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-9mnq16x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-9mnq16x","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"民族主义似乎为一种民族比其他所有民族优越并希望在制度上完善推进这一现状的主义。起源或许是远古的“非我族类其心必异”，也有可能是人对种族间差异深藏的恐惧的外化。你觉得会猜疑一只蛇的善意。这可能更跟基因有关。同时因为人总是倾向于简化认识，对个体的坏的印象可能会推广到全体上。差异不利于凝结共识，在审美上可能导致社会的撕裂（黄种人白人基本都认为黑色为丑陋，不过显然黑人不应该这么想）。宗教可能出现冲突，多元化的协调可能需要额外的资源。多民族往往伴随着入侵和奴役的历史，伴随着历史中长期的压迫与仇恨，歧视。而这很难通过理性来进行调和。"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-7233i4h","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-7233i4h","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-kncrynp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-kncrynp","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国家的建立首先取决于投身创立的人是否能获得事实上统治和独立的权力（那个什么最近在德国被抓获的第几罗马？就是独立战争）。其次是保持经济。宗教与文化，结盟问题。认同与合法性，国防，土地人口规模，周围环境，历史积怨，"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-c4e6zo3","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-c4e6zo3","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-jmhlkja","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-jmhlkja","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"好的但不稳定，解体或失序"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-yyydpae","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-yyydpae","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-odb1ld3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-odb1ld3","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"极权，权威，公有化；？（前者是无法统治，腐败和罪恶横行，后者是无法治理，无全国性的政府。差异：程度不同）"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-5fc7l37","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-5fc7l37","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-k6q3mbz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-k6q3mbz","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"可能吧？"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-jljkq7d","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-jljkq7d","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-ku697z8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-ku697z8","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"？"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-3bwkil8","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-3bwkil8","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-10dtfjl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-10dtfjl","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"？"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-od6x9qu","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-od6x9qu","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-huvuacv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-huvuacv","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"能也应该"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-07t6fqq","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-07t6fqq","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010424-3m1poas","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-3m1poas","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"像英国女皇那样？还是宪法与事实不符？天皇？（象征性政策就是极少投入不过让人满意）"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-y0naop4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-y0naop4","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“所有国家都享有主权和独立，但一些国家比其他国家拥有更多的主权和独立”"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-bmun637","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-bmun637","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“当选举权突然降临在毫无准备的百姓面前时，结果很少会是民主。”"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-ddtying","Type":"NodeThematicBreak","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-ddtying","updated":"20241011010424"}},{"ID":"20241011010424-tdtx7qv","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-tdtx7qv","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宪法"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-834vgi1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-834vgi1","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"日本宪法的特点是1.主权在民2.三权分立3.反对战争"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-439sm2i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-439sm2i","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"有些国家没有成文宪法但也保障了人权，比如英国，凭借对传统的敬畏和拥护。"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-uipsr7v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-uipsr7v","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宪法中不应该包括具体的政治经济措施，不然恐怕很难实行"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-rj92ka9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-rj92ka9","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宪法太过于重要以至于不能进行实验"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-4j4hs4u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-4j4hs4u","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宪法表述了国家的目标，确定了国家的权力结构，也表现统治集团的责任感"}]},{"ID":"20241011010424-r9t1lr6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010424-r9t1lr6","updated":"20241011010424"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进而增加其合法性"}]}]}